<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<title>妹妹说紫色很有韵味</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: sans-serif;
			background: #f9f9f9;
			padding: 2em;
			color: #333;
		}

		h1,
		h3 {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.container {
			max-width: 960px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.color-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
			gap: 1.2em;
			margin-top: 2em;
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.color-grid {
				grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 480px) {
			.color-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}

		.color-box {
			border-radius: 8px;
			overflow: hidden;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			transition: transform 0.2s;
		}

		.color-box:hover {
			transform: translateY(-2px);
		}

		.swatch {
			height: 100px;
			width: 100%;
		}

		.info {
			padding: 0.6em;
			background: white;
			font-size: 0.85em;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.name {
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.hex {
			color: #666;
			font-family: monospace;
		}

		.desc {
			font-size: 0.8em;
			color: #888;
			margin-top: 0.3em;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>「妹妹说紫色很有韵味」</h1>
		<h3>紫色系颜色展示（从浅到深）</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			@each(c in PURPLE_COLORS)
			<div class="color-box">
				<div class="swatch" style="background: {{c.hex}}"></div>
				<div class="info">
					<div class="name">{{c.name}}</div>
					<div class="hex">{{ c.hex }}</div>
					<div class="desc">{{ c.nameZh}}, {{ c.desc }}</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			@end
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>